{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"90421-o-arco-iris-visita-a-aldeia","title":"O Arco-Íris Visita a Aldeia","description":"A boy spots a rainbow for the first time. Do you think he knows what it is?","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nadia Morais","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Wiehan de Jager"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/90421-o-arco-iris-visita-a-aldeia"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130934/size3/b03402a311fac713e1fa8e7bf7ffc166.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130934/size6/b03402a311fac713e1fa8e7bf7ffc166.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128920/size6/b3510d62baeeb903ca340137b8172054.jpg","text":"Kobole vivia numa pequena aldeia.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128921/size6/c26b1a933d452dd437d31074ac3d39be.jpg","text":"Uma tarde, Kobole saiu para apanhar maracujá. Aconteceu umacoisa imprevista.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128925/size6/a24e615e4d8ef25d303b10175d6a0a74.jpg","text":"Viu linhas coloridas a atravessar o céu.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128927/size6/7ebd00939980fd00e803f613a0b3c858.jpg","text":"Deixou cair a fruta e correu para casa para contar aos outros habitantes da aldeia.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128928/size6/0b49f701aaf20583cf1bc2e8cb4e06aa.jpg","text":"Encontrou toda a gente na rua. Estavam a olhar para o céu.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128929/size6/cc39c6c1c99b9de71cd55f6f35589140.jpg","text":"Kobole disse: “É um pano bonito, pendurado do céu.” Neno disse: “Não! Acho que é alguém a verter tinta do céu.”","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128930/size6/51639513f0ed966934fbafe9e06a7280.jpg","text":"Algumas pessoas concordaram com Kobole. Outras, acharam que Neno tinha razão. Os dois grupos discutiam.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128933/size6/3cfcbdee2ebfa1b2afc58d50c82cdbb7.jpg","text":"Um homem de uma aldeia distante chegou e disse. “Estão todos errados.”","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128934/size6/89ab7d765960293372547d3a7d5fad0e.jpg","text":"As pessoas gritaram: “Então, o que é?”","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128935/size6/c8c84f7c2696277c09d8da09f82b101e.jpg","text":"O homem estranho disse: “É o arco-íris. Nunca tinham visto o arco-íris?”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128936/size6/99c23119cb42b53ce9cf573ec80346ef.jpg","text":"“O que é um arcoíris?” perguntaram os habitantes da aldeia.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128937/size6/4c44037165a67eddbef1fd7cd6420268.jpg","text":"Neno perguntou: “É teu? Podemos guardá-lo aqui?” mas o homem já tinha ido embora.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":140}}